<br>
I got my characters from completely KoS to Dwarves and Dragons to amiably in about a week and a half.<br>
<br>
To go the other way you just beat the crap outta stuff in SS and WW.<br>
<br>
Alot of the uber guilds just kill whatever they happen to be up for on rotation and worry about the faction later.<br>
<br>
In terms of epuipment, the giant quest armr has the best ac but there are some pretty awesome quest results in the halls of testing.<br>
<br>
If you're not in an uber guild I'd say go pro dragon to start with as you can kit yourself out in Thurgadin armor in no time.  You can always switch to pro giant faction later. <p><html>
